				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">/pet focus -- pet is now in focus mode 
<br />
/pet attack -- pet will focus on mob sent to attack 
<br />
/pet hold -- pet holds and comes back 
<br />
/pet attack -- pet will focus on mob sent to attack 
<br />

<br />
You will never need to /pet focus again unless your pet dies. If you want to have your pet switch targets, just /pet attack.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
